nodes.text: The TurboDyne 99 was a podracer produced by Elsinore-Cordova Engineering prior to the Clone Wars. Podracer Kidd Kareen owned such a pod, which he lent to fellow racer and crush Ahsoka Tano for during the Mon Gazza Speedway. Anakin Skywalker hinted that a stock 99 was better than a stock Solarix-G6.
